import React from 'react';
import './navbar.css';
import {Container, Nav, Navbar} from 'react-bootstrap';

function Navigation() {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar className = "main-navbar" collapseOnSelect expand = "lg" fixed = "top" variant="dark">
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav"></Navbar.Toggle>
                    <Navbar.Collapse>
                        <Nav className = "mr-auto">
                            <Nav.Link className = "" href = "/#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                            
                        </Nav>
                        <Navbar.Brand className = "mx-auto" href="#home">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
                        <Nav>
                            <Nav.Link className = "" href = "/login">Login</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link className = "" href = "/register">Register</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
    </>
    )
}

export default Navigation
